title: 5G network is not Working in Qatar, Ooredoo the network Operator saying google didn't signed with us
content:
Dear support Team,
5G network is working in Qatar with the two network Operators Ooredoo and Vodafone,
I called Ooredoo, they are saying there are many devices working in Qatar but Pixel from Google is not working because Google didn't signed with them regarding the 5G Network. Please help, I bought the pixel 5 because of the 5G.
Regards,
